      "writtenOn": "2018-12-20T03:10:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I expect idempotent nodes to be used only internally. For publicly visible stuff, I prefer redeclaring something (even with exact same properties) to be an error. At very least to avoid copy-paste mistakes (when some code that should have been deleted or changed is mistakenly left as is, identical to something else).",
